description: [``botocore``] Adds support for new options on GraphqlAPIs, Resolvers and  Data Sources for emitting Amazon CloudWatch metrics for enhanced monitoring of AppSync APIs.
[``botocore``] Update cloudwatch client to latest version
[``botocore``] Adding a new option "parameters" for data plane api ExecuteQuery to support running parameterized query via SDK.
[``botocore``] This release adds bill contact support for RegisterDomain, TransferDomain, UpdateDomainContact and GetDomainDetail API.
